headline: 3 Reasons to Sell EL and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Estée Lauder has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 6.6%. The stock now trades at $88.32, marking a 22.6% gain. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
